23:42:27.000Z","msg":"快樂講真未必係問題。可能割蓆唔齊心先係問題。（我冇資格講究竟雨傘運動係點樣失敗。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係過唔到個關口：如果有人死左，我點樣可以照顧到佢哋身邊人嘅感受，以稍為短時間（可能一兩三日）去比佢哋醫治佢哋嘅情緒。<br />\n<br />\n我係好老土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f68c8491a5cf64acbcb68848630aeb864010d6f","tid":1566962,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c70e0e53fc7cb84f44e0049d93e462f82614ac1b","tid":1566962,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f68c8491a5cf64acbcb68848630aeb864010d6f","tid":1566962,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"bed66e13acddc66a3604ad40e232814c9a61cf6a","tid":1566962,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57c30643854610acc8376fe9762245c2fe08cb7e","tid":1566962,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7fd145d37d27590b5037766afbc33cde778173b","tid":1566962,"uid":237284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T23:16:15.000Z","msg":"唱歌同唔嚴肅有咩關係？<br />\n死左人可能性放係度<br />\n大家831後做左咁多野<br />\n又送左一堆頭<br />\n唱國歌就唔莊嚴？唱國歌就玩膠？<br />\n召喚抗爭者歸屬感同互相打氣堅持啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇人話過其他野唔做 講到國歌好似兒歌咁</span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T23:28:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">默哀加唱歌</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咪搞掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"推pls"},{"pid":"77bcb6350e90cfda72ee6715211a13f76cb2f1a9","tid":1566962,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4144b1e0888945e38d89d0e57bd65052dbed94a0","tid":1566962,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T23:13:20.000Z","msg":"人地快樂抗爭緊。<br />\n<br />\n5年前唱今天我<br />\n<br />\n而家唱榮光"},"citedBy":0,"replyT